paragraphs.text:
%python

sql = 'select id, name from sjt_user'
curs.execute(sql)
name_tuple = curs.fetchall()
name_list = []
for name in name_tuple:
    name_list.append(["{}".format(name[0]),name[1]])

### Select form
search_id = z.select("환자를 선택해주세요",name_list,"2")

# Display the original image and overlay it with the face information.
sql = 'select faceId from sjt_user where id = {}'.format(search_id)
curs.execute(sql)
photo_id = curs.fetchall()[0][0]
photo_url = ''
for sub_list in photo_info:
    if sub_list[1] == photo_id:
        photo_url = sub_list[0]
        break
# print(photo_info)
# print(photo_url)
image = Image.open(BytesIO(requests.get(photo_url).content))
plt.figure(figsize=(4, 4))
ax = plt.imshow(image, alpha=0.6)

paragraphs.title: SBP(수축기 혈압)
paragraphs.text:
pid=1
endTime = int(time.time())

# endUnixTime = int(time.mktime(endTime.timetuple()))
startTime =endTime- 1000
# startUnixTime = int(time.mktime(startTime.timetuple()))

sql = 'SELECT sbp, rr, hr, saO2 FROM sjt_device_data WHERE patientId = {} AND from_unixtime({}) < time AND from_unixtime({})'
curs.execute(sql.format(pid,startTime,endTime))

vital_data = curs.fetchall()
time_list = []
vital_list = [[],[],[],[]]
a=0
for i in vital_data[0:100]:
    time_list.append(a)
    for index in range(0,4):
        if index == 1:
            vital_list[index].append(round(float(i[index]),2))
        else:
            vital_list[index].append(i[index])
    a += 1
df_sbp=pd.DataFrame(vital_list[0])
df_sbp.reset_index(level=0, inplace=True)
# vital_list
df_sbp.columns=['Time','SBP']
z.show(df_sbp)

pid = 1
startTime = datetime(2010,7,3,13,7,30)
startUnixTime = int(time.mktime(startTime.timetuple()))
endTime = datetime(2010,7,3,13,12,30)
endUnixTime = int(time.mktime(endTime.timetuple()))
sql = 'SELECT sbp,rr,hr,saO2 FROM sjt_device_data WHERE  patientId = {} AND from_unixtime({}) < time AND from_unixtime({})'
curs.execute(sql.format(pid,startUnixTime,endUnixTime))
vital_data = curs.fetchall()
time_list = []
vital_list = [[],[],[],[]]
a=0
for i in vital_data[0:60]:
    time_list.append(a)
    for index in range(0,4):
        if index == 1:
            vital_list[index].append(round(float(i[index]),2))
        else:
            vital_list[index].append(i[index])
    a += 1
df_sbp=pd.DataFrame(vital_list[0])
df_sbp.reset_index(level=0, inplace=True)
df_sbp.columns=['Time','SBP']
